17:45.926 --> 17:49.259
I know that one.
When they don't believeyou.

17:49.329 --> 17:51.263
Exactly.

17:51.331 --> 17:53.993
So, when I got back,
I got into boat repo.

17:54.068 --> 17:58.869
That was fine for a while till, of course, mywife
passed away, and then things went downhill.

17:58.939 --> 18:00.930
