18:01.008 --> 18:04.444
Virgil's only going to be here
a night, maybe two.

18:04.511 --> 18:07.708
-Where's the hatchet, Mom?
- Try the utility drawer.

18:07.781 --> 18:09.840
I don't want to be an imposition.

18:09.917 --> 18:12.647
- I can sleep out in the back ifyou need.
- I don't mind.

18:12.719 --> 18:16.177
Really, I'd never see Michael at all
ifhe didn't bring his friends over.

18:16.256 --> 18:19.953
I knowwhat that's like. I don't get to see
mydaughter Trudyverymuch either.

18:20.027 --> 18:23.690
Oh. Yeah. It was worse
after he went overseas.

18:23.764 --> 18:26.358
- Then Michael's father died in '98.
- Oh.

18:26.433 --> 18:28.492
- How did you lose your wife?
- Cancer.

18:28.569 --> 18:31.800
- Oh.
- She was a nurse at the V.A.
