22:45.025 --> 22:47.016
Where is he?

22:48.528 --> 22:50.860
He's in my bedroom.

22:51.998 --> 22:54.228
Ugh.

22:54.301 --> 22:57.464
He's lonely, Michael. And so am I.

22:57.537 --> 22:59.562
It's been a long time
sinceyourfather died.

22:59.639 --> 23:03.769
Andsometimes I think it would be good
