23:40.113 --> 23:42.172
[ Chuckling]
Come on, Mike.

23:42.249 --> 23:44.274
That's a glass-half-empty way
of looking at it.

23:44.351 --> 23:46.683
Mason probably stumbled upon
the money smuggling operation...

23:46.753 --> 23:49.654
didn't want to risk pulling
the heist himself.

23:49.723 --> 23:52.021
You were the cutout.
You deliverthe boat, he shoots you...

23:52.092 --> 23:55.289
and 300 gallons ofburning methyl chloride
cleans up the mess.

23:55.362 --> 23:58.297
Jesus. What do I do?

23:58.365 --> 24:02.165
Well, fornow, dump the boat.

24:02.235 --> 24:05.636
- [ Whimpers ]
- You have anyway of reaching these cops?

24:07.407 --> 24:09.375
[ Sighs ]

24:12.045 --> 24:13.979
I got a number.

24:14.047 --> 24:16.413
[ Cell Phone Beeping]

24:16.483 --> 24:19.316
[ Line Ringing ]

24:19.386 --> 24:23.379
Nah, this ain't Virgil.
This is your buddy Homer. Remember me?

24:23.457 --> 24:27.723
Nah, he ain't around. Y'all have to deal
with me now, and I want a meetin'.

24:29.296 --> 24:31.287
[Michael Narrating]
When working a coveridentity...

24:31.364 --> 24:33.855
the safest thing is to let the target
take the lead.

24:33.934 --> 24:37.301
You've got more information than he does.
You want to keep that edge.

24:37.370 --> 24:40.396
Hey, you brought your friends.
Got a little party goin' on here, don't we?

24:40.474 --> 24:43.409
[ Chuckling ]
You want some fries?

24:44.678 --> 24:46.669
How would you like to die chokin' on 'em?

24:46.746 --> 24:50.113
Oh, they're good.
Not that good, but they're good.

24:51.585 --> 24:54.383
Now, see, that is just unfriendly.

24:54.454 --> 24:57.389
Where's Virgil?

25:12.372 --> 25:14.363
Seems a shame just to dump it.

25:14.441 --> 25:16.534
- It is a nice boat.
- Yeah, it's a nice boat.

25:16.610 --> 25:20.637
It's a nice boat with a big hole in the deck
and a bunch of guys with guns looking for it.

25:20.714 --> 25:23.478
Oh, yeah. Thankyou, Sam.

25:23.550 --> 25:28.419
Yeah. Virg, when this is over,
ifwe're not dead, thank me then.

25:28.488 --> 25:30.422
All right, Sam.

25:30.490 --> 25:33.482
I don't know where he is.
He's holed up somewhere.

25:33.560 --> 25:36.222
- Listen, we got a real problem here.
- Well, that's right.

25:36.296 --> 25:40.323
We want out ofthis, but those guys we took
the boat from, they're comin' after us.

25:40.400 --> 25:43.460
