26:23.710 --> 26:25.507
Talk to theJamaicans.

26:26.780 --> 26:28.771
I'll seeyou tomorrow.

26:43.930 --> 26:45.830
- [ Gunfire]
- Virg, get down!

27:02.382 --> 27:04.577
[ Virgil ]
How in the hell did they find us?

27:04.651 --> 27:06.812
[ Sam ]
Must have had a backup G.P.S. tracker.

27:08.054 --> 27:09.681
It ain't here!

27:11.424 --> 27:12.857
Damn!

27:17.464 --> 27:19.557
What happened? You look awful.

27:19.633 --> 27:21.794
Trust me, sweet thing.
You'd rather not know.

27:21.868 --> 27:24.359
I can't believe we didn't find
that other tracking device.

27:24.437 --> 27:26.428
- Andre's good.
- And that's bad.

27:26.506 --> 27:28.497
Doyou want something to drink?

27:28.575 --> 27:30.702
Yeah, that sounds good.
Maybe a scotch.

27:30.777 --> 27:33.268
I wouldn't mind a little somethin',
ifyou're gonna go--

27:33.346 --> 27:36.838
Sam, not now.
We need to talk alone, Mom.

27:37.951 --> 27:40.385
